*.pyc
.pytest_cache/

# ONNX embedding model (~90MB) — third-party (sentence-transformers/all-MiniLM-L6-v2),
# re-downloadable via `python scripts/export_onnx_model.py`, not ours to ship.
artifacts/all-MiniLM-L6-v2/

# artifacts/models/*.joblib and artifacts/drain3_state/*.bin are NOT ignored —
# those are our own trained per-dataset baselines (see README.md's eval
# table), shipped so a fresh install can seed detection immediately
# (LogPipeline.seed_from_pretrained) instead of cold-starting with nothing.

# third-party datasets: fetch per datasets/SOURCES.md, don't commit
datasets/*.tar.gz
datasets/*.zip
datasets/_extracted/
datasets/_nginx_raw/
